thread.title: Sandra

author: Sandra
title: Sandra
text: They sent us the code within 24hrs even though it should've taken 3 days. We typed the code in but it war unsuccessful. We contracted cellunlocker and got a promt email back with things to try as making sure it's the original software and also trying a factory reset. It still didn't work. We email led them back again and again got a promt answer with a detailed description od how to get into the developer menu and what to do. We did that, tried the unlock code again and Bingo! It worked. Very nice and knowledgeable staff who don't leave you hanging
